    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-03-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-03-03T23:30:00-05:00" n="1311"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1311">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.115/67.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consular Agent <persName type="from">Lewis</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Los Mochis</hi>
                        </placeName> (<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1914-03-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1914-03-04T00:00:00-04:30">
                            <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                        </date>
                        <hi rend="italic">; received March 5, 1914</hi>).</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>You message 27th. Unable secure confirmation of statement regarding demand by
                    Carranza. If such was made interested parties evidently not desirous of having
                    matter known.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lewis</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
